</li></ul></li>
<li><a href="../tag/t5d.html"><span class="tagL">T5D: Formal Methods</span></a><ul><li> It relies on formal methods (definitions/proofs/semantic properties) beyond informal description.
</li></ul></li>
<li><a href="../tag/t1d.html"><span class="tagL">T1D: Composition</span></a><ul><li> It emphasizes modularity/composition/integration (embedding or coordinating language components).
